---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Lotus Rose Counseling in Orem, UT | Our Story"
  description="Learn about Lotus Rose Counseling — a therapy practice in Orem, Utah founded by Joy Bouchard, LCSW, specializing in trauma, postpartum, grief, and EMDR therapy."
>

  <!-- Full-Bleed Hero -->
  <section class="hero-fullbleed">
    <div class="hero-fullbleed-bg">
      <img src="/florals/floral-contact.jpg" alt="Dried flowers — Lotus Rose Counseling story" width="1920" height="1080" fetchpriority="high" />
    </div>
    <div class="hero-fullbleed-overlay"></div>
    <div class="hero-fullbleed-content">
      <p class="section-label">Our Story</p>
      <h1>Why "Lotus Rose"?</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">Two symbols of strength, resilience, and the ability to bloom after adversity.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Split: Joy's Story -->
  <div class="split-section">
    <div class="split-content">
      <p class="section-label">Joy's Story</p>
      <h2>"I Know What It's Like to Need Help in That Period of Time"</h2>
      <p>Joy Bouchard founded Lotus Rose because she's lived the struggle. As a mother of three, she has her own journey with birth trauma, postpartum depression, and postpartum anxiety — each child bringing a different experience.</p>
      <p>She knows what it's like to be searching for someone you can talk to, someone who can give guidance on how to navigate the hardest chapters of motherhood. That's why she created a place that wasn't just specialized — but that <strong>felt</strong> safe.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="split-image">
      <img src="/photos/joy-bouchard.jpg" alt="Joy Bouchard, LCSW — founder of Lotus Rose Counseling" width="800" height="800" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Pull Quote -->
  <section class="bg-cream">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-container">
        <div class="pull-quote">
          <p>"I wanted to create a place that was very safe, that felt warm and welcoming. All of our clinicians are trained in how to help specifically with women's issues. I wanted it to be a safe haven."</p>
          <cite>Joy Bouchard, LCSW — Founder</cite>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Split Reverse: What She's Passionate About -->
  <div class="split-section split-section--reverse">
    <div class="split-content">
      <p class="section-label">What Drives Us</p>
      <h2>The Two Things Joy Loves Treating Most</h2>
      <p><strong>Infant loss.</strong> With her own life experience in helping women who've lost an infant or newborn, Joy loves holding space for women during one of the hardest periods of life.</p>
      <p><strong>Childhood abuse resurfacing in motherhood.</strong> Women come in for postpartum depression and discover there's unprocessed trauma from their childhood underneath. Joy found these two areas deeply overlap — and treating them together is what she's most passionate about.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="split-image">
      <img src="/photos/office-5.jpg" alt="Comfortable therapy environment at Lotus Rose Counseling" width="800" height="600" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- What Makes Us Different -->
  <section class="bg-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-container">
        <p class="section-label">What Makes Us Different</p>
        <h2>Women's Mental Health Is Our Specialty. It's What We Do Best.</h2>
        <p>A lot of practices say they see women for postpartum or perinatal issues — but they also see everyone else for everything else. At Lotus Rose, women's mental health is our core focus. We also work with teens and children — especially those navigating grief, loss, trauma, and behavioral challenges.</p>
        <p>Every therapist is trained in trauma treatment. Every continuing education course is chosen specifically to get better at treating women's issues. The space itself was designed to feel like a safe haven — warm, welcoming, and nothing like a clinical office.</p>

        <div class="highlight-box">
          <h4>What We Believe</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>The therapeutic relationship is the foundation — you need to feel safe before you can heal</li>
            <li>Therapy isn't just talking — there's training, technique, and expertise behind it</li>
            <li>Healing takes time — most clients work with us for 6-12 months, and that's normal</li>
            <li>There's room for humor in hard work — the space needs to feel human</li>
            <li>You should never feel locked in — no contracts, no pressure, find the right fit</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Full-Width Photo Break -->
  <div class="photo-break">
    <img src="/photos/office-2.jpg" alt="Lotus Rose Counseling therapy room" width="1920" height="800" loading="lazy" />
  </div>

  <!-- Who We Serve -->
  <section class="bg-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-container">
        <p class="section-label">Who We Work With</p>
        <h2>Women Navigating Life's Hardest Chapters</h2>
        <p>Our practice serves women dealing with perinatal mental health disorders — postpartum depression, birth trauma, infant loss, and the full spectrum of postpartum mood and anxiety. We also specialize in childhood abuse recovery, especially when it resurfaces during motherhood.</p>
        <p>Beyond that, we help women navigating difficult relationships, physical and sexual abuse, grief and loss, anxiety, depression, and the identity shifts that come with major life transitions. For teens and children, we treat behavioral challenges, anxiety, trauma, and self-esteem struggles.</p>
        <p>Whether you're a new mom with intrusive thoughts, a woman processing decades-old trauma, or a teenager navigating hard changes — there's a therapist at Lotus Rose who has specific training for your experience.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Office Gallery -->
  <section class="bg-cream">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-container text-center">
        <p class="section-label">Our Space</p>
        <h2>A Place That Feels Like Home</h2>
        <p>Located in a cozy basement space under Forever by Ash in Orem. Joy put a lot of work into making every room feel warm, inviting, and nothing like a clinical setting.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="photo-grid" style="margin-top: 40px;">
        <img src="/photos/office-1.jpg" alt="Therapy room at Lotus Rose Counseling in Orem, Utah" width="768" height="512" loading="lazy" />
        <img src="/photos/office-3.jpg" alt="Warm therapy space at Lotus Rose Counseling" width="768" height="512" loading="lazy" />
        <img src="/photos/office-5.jpg" alt="Lotus Rose Counseling office interior" width="768" height="512" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Ready to Begin Your Healing Journey?</h2>
      <p>Schedule a free 15-minute consultation to find the right therapist for you.</p>
      <div class="btn-group" style="justify-content: center;">
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn-primary">Schedule Free Consultation</a>
        <a href="tel:+18016424244" class="btn-secondary">Call (801) 642-4244</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
